channel.title: 2 Questions With Objects
channel.description: Ok, first, what client shows you the object id by right clicking it? Second, can anybody tell me the object id of the ladder in the grand tree? Thanks!

item.title: 2 Questions With Objects
item.dc:creator: @thebigpurpleglob thebigpurpleglob
item.description:
@thebigpurpleglob wrote:

Theres no need to get the client that shows the object ID by right clicking it, you can just download a Objects list, but Moparscape’s Webclient does that, and i’m almost positive Delta clients do that aswell but im not sure on the delta one, any ladder will work also if you wan’t to code in a ladder that will lead you to the next floor of the grand tree, just make sure you go into objects.cfg (or w/e file you have for objects) and make sure it takes you up to H2 (HIGHT 2).
